# UI Development Patterns

## Main Dashboard
- [app/ui/main_dashboard.py](mdc:app/ui/main_dashboard.py) - Central UI orchestrator
- Use Tkinter with ttk widgets for modern appearance
- Implement proper threading for camera operations to avoid UI freezing

## UI Components
- [app/ui/student_registration.py](mdc:app/ui/student_registration.py) - Student registration interface
- [app/ui/student_management.py](mdc:app/ui/student_management.py) - Student data management
- [app/ui/attendance_marking.py](mdc:app/ui/attendance_marking.py) - Attendance marking interface
- [app/ui/attendance_history.py](mdc:app/ui/attendance_history.py) - Attendance history viewer

## UI Guidelines
- Use consistent color scheme: background '#f0f0f0', primary colors from constants
- Implement proper error handling with user-friendly messageboxes
- Use threading for all camera and detection operations
- Follow responsive design principles for different screen sizes
- Use PIL.ImageTk for efficient image display in Tkinter

## Camera Integration
- Use [app/utils/camera_utils.py](mdc:app/utils/camera_utils.py) for camera management
- Implement proper camera initialization and cleanup
- Handle camera switching and resolution changes gracefully